'''Karl August Erich Obst''' (13 September 1886 – 9 June 1981) was a [[Germany|German]] [[geographer]] and [[Geopolitics|geopolitician]]. Between 1924 and 1944 he was the editor of the German geopolitical magazine ''"Zeitschrift fur Geopolitik"''.

