* Westernmost Point &mdash; [[Punta de la Orchilla]], [[El Hierro]], [[Canary Islands]] at {{coord|27|43|N|18|09|W|region:ES_type:landmark|name=Punta de la Orchilla (Westernmost point)}}
* Easternmost Point &mdash; La Mola Island, [[Mahón]], [[Menorca]] at {{coord|39|52|N|4|19|E|region:ES_type:isle|name=La Mola Island (Easternmost point)}}
* Highest Point &mdash; [[El Teide]] 3,718 m, [[Tenerife]]
* Point furthest from the coast (Iberian Pole of Inaccessibility) {{coord|39.99|N|4.51|W|region:ES_type:landmark|name=Iberian Pole of Inaccessibility}}

