[[Image:Mosebacke Terrass Stockholm 2005-06-06.jpg|thumb|right|250px|A corner of the square at Mosebacke]]
'''Mosebacke''' (''Moses Hill'') is an area in [[Södermalm]] in [[Stockholm]], [[Sweden]] known for venues where cultural events take place. There are restaurants, a theater ([[Södra teatern]]) and stages where local celebrities like [[Cornelis Vreeswijk]] have performed.

